## GetTasksIDRunsRequest.afterTime property

A timestamp ([RFC3339 date/time format](https://docs.influxdata.com/influxdb/v2.3/reference/glossary/#rfc3339-timestamp)<!-- -->). Only returns runs scheduled after this time.

```typescript
afterTime?: string;
```
